1. 问题: 查询2022年3月2日‘其他’车型在各个服务区的车辆数量，并关联显示服务区名称（来自bss_service_area表）。
   原始错误: 字段 sa.name 不存在
LINE 1: EXPLAIN SELECT sa.name AS "服务区名称", cdc.customer_count A...
                       ^
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT sa.service_area_name AS "服务区名称", cdc.customer_count AS "车辆数量" FROM public.bss_car_day_count cdc JOIN public.bss_service_area sa ON cdc.service_area_id = sa.id WHERE cdc.count_date = '2022-03-02' AND cdc.car_type = '其他' AND cdc.delete_ts IS NULL AND sa.delete_ts IS NULL;
----------------------------------------

2. 问题: 统计每条路线关联的服务区数量，并按服务区数量降序排列。
   原始错误: 字段 r.路线名称 不存在
LINE 1: EXPLAIN SELECT r."路线名称", COUNT(l.service_area_id) AS "服...
                       ^
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT r.route_name AS "路线名称", COUNT(l.service_area_id) AS "服务区数量" FROM public.bss_section_route r INNER JOIN public.bss_section_route_area_link l ON r.id = l.section_route_id WHERE r.delete_ts IS NULL GROUP BY r.route_name ORDER BY "服务区数量" DESC;
----------------------------------------

3. 问题: 查询路段名称为'昌栗'的所有服务区名称（需通过路段-路线关联表和服务区关联表联合获取）。
   原始错误: 字段 sa.服务区名称 不存在
LINE 1: EXPLAIN SELECT sa."服务区名称" FROM public.bss_section_route...
                       ^
   修复后SQL:
   SELECT sa.service_area_name FROM public.bss_section_route sr INNER JOIN public.bss_section_route_area_link sral ON sr.id = sral.section_route_id INNER JOIN public.bss_service_area sa ON sral.service_area_id = sa.id WHERE sr.section_name = '昌栗' AND sr.delete_ts IS NULL;
----------------------------------------

